<content>1: # Build stage
2: FROM node:18-alpine AS builder
3: 
4: WORKDIR /app
5: 
6: COPY package*.json ./
7: RUN npm ci
8: COPY tsconfig.json ./
9: COPY . .
10: RUN npx tsc
11: 
12: # Production stage
13: FROM node:18-alpine
14: 
15: WORKDIR /app
16: 
17: COPY --from=builder /app/package*.json ./
18: COPY --from=builder /app/dist ./dist
19: COPY --from=builder /app/node_modules ./node_modules
20: 
21: ENV NODE_ENV=production
22: 
23: EXPOSE 3000
24: 
25: RUN addgroup -g 1001 -S nodejs && \
26:     adduser -S nodejs -u 1001 && \
27:     chown -R nodejs:nodejs /app
28: 
29: USER nodejs
30: 
31: CMD ["node", "dist/index.js"]
32: 
33: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
34:   CMD node -e "require('http').get('http://localhost:3000/health', (r) => {process.exit(r.statusCode === 200 ? 0 : 1)})"

# Build stage
FROM node:18-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /app

COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci
COPY tsconfig.json ./
COPY . .
RUN npx tsc

# Production stage
FROM node:18-alpine

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder /app/package*.json ./
COPY --from=builder /app/dist ./dist
COPY --from=builder /app/node_modules ./node_modules

ENV NODE_ENV=production

EXPOSE 3000

RUN addgroup -g 1001 -S nodejs && \
    adduser -S nodejs -u 1001 && \
    chown -R nodejs:nodejs /app

USER nodejs

CMD ["node", "dist/index.js"]

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
  CMD node -e "require('http').get('http://localhost:3000/health', (r) => {process.exit(r.statusCode === 200 ? 0 : 1)})"
